title: Jenna Jameson goes on Twitter rant slamming Muslims | Daily Mail Online
text: Pregnant Jenna Jameson goes on Twitter rant defending the KKK and slamming Muslims The former porn star and recent Jewish convert lashed out against Muslims on Twitter on Tuesday In her nearly four-hour long diatribe, Jameson labeled Islam as inherently homophobic and sexist She also proclaimed the existence of so-called Muslim rape gangs in Europe In another tweet, she favorably compared the KKK to Muslim extremists Jameson is currently expecting a child with her fiance, Israeli jeweler Lior Bitton Published: 13:50 GMT, 22 February 2017 | Updated: 16:09 GMT, 22 February 2017 75 shares
